    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Burgie's cozy kitchen</strong> 是一款关于经营你自己的街头汉堡店的小型游戏。享受其温馨放松的风格，当然也有一些可爱而混乱的时刻！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>为顾客烹饪并提升你的汉堡店 🍔</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314340/extras/2011c10e427359d63ffe69f04a97e605.poster.avif?t=1768985240\" width=600 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314340/extras/2011c10e427359d63ffe69f04a97e605.webm?t=1768985240\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314340/extras/2011c10e427359d63ffe69f04a97e605.mp4?t=1768985240\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌸 <strong>放松的游戏</strong>，美丽而温馨， <strong>可以按照你自己的节奏进行游戏</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>💡 简单的机制</strong>，非常精致， <strong>彼此之间紧密相连</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🤫 <strong>多种隐藏机制</strong>，随着你的进展逐步发现。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🍂 有趣的 <strong>物理系统</strong>，使一切更加真实和有趣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💻 你可以 <strong>主动游戏或将其最小化</strong>， <strong>在桌面上等待新的订单到来</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⏱ <strong>4~8 小时的内容</strong>，逐步解锁。最后还有一个评分榜，供那些想要继续游戏的玩家使用。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>在工作或进行其他活动时玩游戏 ✍</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314340/extras/e2d372fb49a40ba931374a85cde49a06.poster.avif?t=1768985240\" width=600 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314340/extras/e2d372fb49a40ba931374a85cde49a06.webm?t=1768985240\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314340/extras/e2d372fb49a40ba931374a85cde49a06.mp4?t=1768985240\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这款游戏允许你 <strong>将柜台最小化到屏幕的一角</strong>，这样你可以在等待新订单的同时专注于其他任务。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当有新订单到来时，会响铃提醒你准备汉堡并尽可能好地服务顾客。 <strong>小费和厨房的提升取决于他们的评价！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>不同的游戏模式 🕹</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314340/extras/2362ce182aebce503a796def45dfc96e.poster.avif?t=1768985240\" width=600 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314340/extras/2362ce182aebce503a796def45dfc96e.webm?t=1768985240\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314340/extras/2362ce182aebce503a796def45dfc96e.mp4?t=1768985240\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🔥 紧张模式</strong>：与不断光顾且有些不耐烦的顾客积极互动。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>☕ 放松模式</strong>：将游戏最小化，每 5–15 分钟服务一次顾客， <strong>以小休息的方式丰富你的一天</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>📚 番茄钟模式</strong>：将游戏最小化， <strong>设置时间</strong>，当你需要休息时，会有新的顾客提醒你。 <strong>是一个理想的游戏化集中注意力工具</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🤩 主播模式</strong>：将上述任意模式与你的直播结合。 <strong>你的观众可以通过直播聊天</strong> 使用简单的命令加入，并向你提出他们能想到的最疯狂的订单。 <strong>如果你做错了，他们也会抱怨！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>与观众聊天互动：支持 Twitch、YouTube、Kick 和 Tiktok 聊天集成 💬</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314340/extras/69dcf839e67ebb8628bd3219172cc834.poster.avif?t=1768985240\" width=600 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314340/extras/69dcf839e67ebb8628bd3219172cc834.webm?t=1768985240\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314340/extras/69dcf839e67ebb8628bd3219172cc834.mp4?t=1768985240\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以将游戏连接到你的 <strong>YouTube、Kick、Tiktok 或 Twitch 聊天</strong>，以接收你自己的观众和他们的订单。 <strong>你可以与每位观众单独聊天</strong>，为他们提供你想要的食物，还有更多！他们的评价也会影响你的评分，帮助你（或不帮助你）在全球主播排行榜上攀升。</p>",
